org.cpsolver.studentsct.online.selection

Class SuggestionSelection

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.studentsct.heuristics.selection.BranchBoundSelection
      • org.cpsolver.studentsct.online.selection.SuggestionSelection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NeighbourSelection<Request,Enrollment>, InfoProvider<Request,Enrollment>, SolverListener<Request,Enrollment>, OnlineSectioningSelection

    public class SuggestionSelection
extends BranchBoundSelection
implements OnlineSectioningSelection
    Online student sectioning algorithm based on the BranchBoundSelection of the batch solver. The selections adds the ability to provide required free times and sections and to prefer certain sections. If a course request has preferred sections, StudentWeights.PreferenceFactor parameter is used to penalize selection of a non-preferred section.
    Version:
    StudentSct 1.3 (Student Sectioning)
